      "content": "Here are a few caption options that balance professionalism with a welcoming vibe:  \n\"Crafting great coffee together while celebrating our shared diversity. At our boutique shop, every guest brings a unique story that fuels our inclusive community. Join us as we pour warmth and welcome into every conversation.\"  \n\"Coffee tastes better when shared among all kinds of people. We are proud to build a space where diversity thrives, making each visitor feel seen and valued. Come say hi and let us make your day brighter.\"  \n\"Our roast is special, and so is the diverse family gathered to enjoy it every day. As a small shop rooted in inclusion, we believe how we welcome others shapes the industry. Let's raise our cups to unity.\"  \n\nFeel free to tweak any of these to better match your brand voice!",
