      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here are a few stronger options that explicitly frame equity as a business necessity in 2024:\n\n\"True business excellence in 2024 requires us to do more than just tolerate difference; we must actively dismantle barriers and champion equity within our supply chain and our community. Our commitment to inclusion is not just our foundation, but a strategic imperative that drives innovation and ensures no one is left behind. We stand firmly for a future where diversity is not an option, but the only way to serve everyone fairly.\"\n\n\"Equity is no longer a nice-to-have metric for excellence, it is the engine that powers a sustainable business in today's market. At our cafe, we are committed to operationalizing these values by championing underrepresented voices and ensuring every interaction reflects genuine fairness. Let's choose a future where our commitment to justice fuels our greatest success.\"\n\n\"Riding the wave of rising inequality demands that we lead by example, turning our commitment to equity into a tangible reality for our staff and guests alike. We are dedicated to building a business model where diversity is celebrated and justice is the standard, not the exception. Your tip helps us don't just roast better coffee, but also fortify our commitment to a fairer",
